# Web3Forms access key — powers the Quote, Contact and Newsletter forms.
#
# How to get one (free, ~1 minute):
#   1. Go to https://web3forms.com
#   2. Enter the email where you want to RECEIVE submissions
#      (e.g. zenitglobe@gmail.com) and click "Create Access Key".
#   3. Check that inbox for the access key (a UUID).
#   4. Copy this file to ".env", paste the key below, and rebuild.
#
# Note: this key is safe to expose in the frontend — that's how Web3Forms
# is designed to work. It only allows sending mail to YOUR verified address.
VITE_WEB3FORMS_KEY=your-access-key-here
